         </title><para id="v110168637">The <guilabel moreinfo="none">Threat Activity</guilabel> widget shows you how the overall threat landscape  has changed over time. You can choose the time frame and monitor the data for spikes in activity. </para><para id="v110168638">You can determine whether the overall health of your endpoints is  increasing or decreasing. And you can analyze repeating trends to find out if spikes are related to particular calendar dates or business conditions. For example, a sudden increase in threat activity might correspond to the enrollment of a large number of devices during that time. </para><para id="v110168641">
